lines: 1. Nimenye as' egetunwa,As' omobaso 'muya;'Mochie bw'obuya obonge,Aase ay'omogambi.Ens' ere n' omoik' omuya,Ebisicha bikwama,Ase engegu y'ensoko,bitari kwoma rinde.
2. Natonywe 'mache 'chinsoko,Ense 'nyia toramenye;Amache ay'obogimaTonywe toisaneke;Titokoba na erang'o,Gose 'gwechanda kondeGatwanyorire emonga,Etari gosareka.
3. Moinyore 'mosalaba,'Monene abambetwe,Ase emechando y'ense,Atworokie enchera;Monene 'torangeirie,Yoimokie 'mosalaba,Nakoroseirie 'nchera,Oraike Igoro.
